OL,3,CNon-statutory inquiry into alleged
OL,4,Cmistreatment at asylum centre set for
OL,5,CMarch
OL,7,FThe alleged mistreatment of asylum
OL,8,Fseekers at Manston processing centre
OL,9,Fin Kent, will be investigated as part
OL,10,Fof an independent inquiry set to open
OL,11,Fnext month, the Government has
OL,12,Fannounced.
OL,14,FHome Office minister Dame Angela Eagle
OL,15,Fsaid the probe, which was first
OL,16,Fapproved under the former Tory
OL,17,Fgovernment, would start on March 17.
