OL,3,CNon-statutory inquiry into alleged
OL,4,Cmistreatment at asylum centre set for
OL,5,CMarch
OL,7,FLawyers for some of the migrants who
OL,8,Fwere held at the site had argued for a
OL,9,Fstatutory inquiry, which can compel
OL,10,Fwitnesses to give evidence under oath,
OL,11,Fand to which the previous
OL,12,Fadministration agreed last March.
OL,14,FBut Home Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,15,Fopted instead for a non-statutory
OL,16,Finquiry, reversing her predecessor
OL,17,FJames Cleverly's decision.
