OL,3,CNon-statutory inquiry into alleged
OL,4,Cmistreatment at asylum centre set for
OL,5,CMarch
OL,7,FAnnouncing new details of the
OL,8,Finvestigation on Wednesday, Dame
OL,9,FAngela said it would be chaired by
OL,10,FSophie Cartwright KC, a senior
OL,11,Fbarrister with past experience of
OL,12,Finquests and inquiries.
OL,14,FThe investigation will look at the
OL,15,F"decisions, actions and circumstances
OL,16,Fwhich led to" the conditions at
OL,17,FManston, and examine whether there are
OL,18,F"lessons to be learned" regarding the
OL,19,FHome Office's handling of the
OL,20,Fincident, she said.
