OL,4,Cmistreatment at asylum centre set for
OL,5,CMarch
OL,7,FThe situation at Manston was said to
OL,8,Fhave reached a nadir in 2022 after
OL,9,Fconcerns were raised about
OL,10,Fovercrowding at the site, which has a
OL,11,F1,600-person capacity but was holding
OL,12,F4,000 people in November that year.
OL,14,FHealth authorities said at the time
OL,15,Fthat migrants at the site, which is
OL,16,Fused to process people who have
OL,17,Farrived by small boats to the UK,
OL,18,Fwould be vaccinated against diphtheria
OL,19,Fafter an outbreak of the highly
OL,20,Fcontagious disease in England.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
