OL,7,FLawyers acting for some 96 asylum
OL,8,Fseekers at the centre have said they
OL,9,Fhad faced "egregious conditions",
OL,10,Fincluding "instances of humiliation",
OL,11,Fthat affected their "personal hygiene
OL,12,Fand wellbeing".
