OL,7,FDame Angela said on Wednesday: "The
OL,8,FGovernment will make no comment on
OL,9,Fissues which are now in the purview of
OL,10,Fthe inquiry until it has concluded,
OL,11,Fbut we will encourage all current and
OL,12,Fformer public officials with evidence
OL,13,Fto provide to the inquiry to co-
OL,14,Foperate with its requests for
OL,15,Fassistance."
